{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01R4kwT1VkyWRc7CiHzv7ice","type":"tool_result","content":"# cockroachdb/expose-ingress\n# Expose CockroachDB DB Console via HTTPS ingress and SQL traffic via TCP ingress\n\nprompt: |\n  A 3-node CockroachDB cluster is running in the cockroachdb namespace. The\n  ingress-nginx controller is already installed and running in ingress-nginx.\n\n  Your task:\n  - Make the DB Console reachable at https://{{params.ui_host}} (TLS required).\n  - Expose SQL traffic via ingress-nginx on TCP port {{params.sql_port}}.\n\n  Notes:\n  - Use the {{params.ingress_class_name}} ingress class.\n  - SQL uses a TCP protocol (not HTTP).\n\n  Useful commands:\n  ```bash\n  kubectl -n cockroachdb get svc,ingress\n  kubectl -n ingress-nginx get cm\n  ```\n\nparams:\n  ui_host:\n    default: crdb-ui.example.com\n    description: Hostname at which the DB Console must be reachable over HTTPS\n  sql_port:\n    default: 26257\n    description: TCP port on which SQL traffic is exposed via ingress\n  ingress_class_name:\n    default: nginx\n    description: Ingress class used for the exposed routes\n\nnamespace_contract:\n  required_roles: []\n\nmetrics:\n  - time_to_first_mutation\n\npreconditionUnits:\n  - name: crdb_env_ready\n    on_probe_fail: skip\n    probe:\n      - command: \"kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods 2>/dev/null | grep -c Running\"\n        timeout_sec: 10\n    apply:\n      - command: \"/bin/sh -c 'kubectl delete namespace cockroachdb --ignore-not-found=true; kubectl wait --for=delete namespace/cockroachdb --timeout=120s || true'\"\n        sleep: 2\n      - command: \"/bin/sh -c 'kubectl create namespace ingress-nginx --dry-run=client -o yaml | kubectl apply -f -'\"\n        sleep: 0\n      - command: \"kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/main/deploy/static/provider/kind/deploy.yaml\"\n        sleep: 90\n      - command: \"kubectl -n ingress-nginx rollout status deploy/ingress-nginx-controller --timeout=120s\"\n        sleep: 2\n      - command: \"kubectl -n ingress-nginx patch deployment ingress-nginx-controller --type=json -p '[{\\\"op\\\":\\\"add\\\",\\\"path\\\":\\\"/spec/template/spec/containers/0/args/-\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"--watch-ingress-without-class=false\\\"}]'\"\n        sleep: 1\n      - command: \"kubectl -n ingress-nginx rollout status deploy/ingress-nginx-controller --timeout=120s\"\n        sleep: 2\n      - command: \"kubectl create namespace cockroachdb\"\n        sleep: 1\n      - command: \"kubectl -n cockroachdb apply -f cases/cockroachdb/expose-ingress/resource/\"\n        sleep: 5\n      - command: \"/bin/sh -c 'for i in $(seq 1 30); do count=$(kubectl -n cockroachdb get pod -l app.kubernetes.io/name=cockroachdb --no-headers 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d \\\" \\\"); if [ \\\"${count}\\\" -ge 1 ]; then exit 0; fi; sleep 2; done; exit 1'\"\n        sleep: 1\n      - command: \"kubectl -n cockroachdb wait --for=jsonpath={.status.phase}=Running pod -l app.kubernetes.io/name=cockroachdb --timeout=300s\"\n        sleep: 5\n      - command: \"/bin/sh -c 'for i in $(seq 1 30); do kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach init --insecure --host=crdb-cluster-0.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local && exit 0; sleep 3; done; exit 1'\"\n        sleep: 2\n      - command: \"kubectl -n cockroachdb wait --for=condition=ready pod -l app.kubernetes.io/name=cockroachdb --timeout=300s\"\n        sleep: 10\n      - command: \"kubectl -n cockroachdb wait --for=condition=Ready pod/curl-test --timeout=60s\"\n        sleep: 2\n    verify:\n      - command: \"kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach sql --insecure -e 'SELECT 1;' 2>/dev/null\"\n        timeout_sec: 15\n\noracle:\n  verify:\n    commands:\n      - command: \"python3 cases/cockroachdb/expose-ingress/oracle/oracle.py\"\n        timeout_sec: 60","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"89b5e537-5eda-44ee-af1e-4f18b36efdbc","uuid":"a284295a-6bfa-47a5-972c-45f0b221d992","timestamp":"2026-06-15T00:54:43.477Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"# cockroachdb/expose-ingress\n# Expose CockroachDB DB Console via HTTPS ingress and SQL traffic via TCP ingress\n\nprompt: |\n  A 3-node CockroachDB cluster is running in the cockroachdb namespace. The\n  ingress-nginx controller is already installed and running in ingress-nginx.\n\n  Your task:\n  - Make the DB Console reachable at https://{{params.ui_host}} (TLS required).\n  - Expose SQL traffic via ingress-nginx on TCP port {{params.sql_port}}.\n\n  Notes:\n  - Use the {{params.ingress_class_name}} ingress class.\n  - SQL uses a TCP protocol (not HTTP).\n\n  Useful commands:\n  ```bash\n  kubectl -n cockroachdb get svc,ingress\n  kubectl -n ingress-nginx get cm\n  ```\n\nparams:\n  ui_host:\n    default: crdb-ui.example.com\n    description: Hostname at which the DB Console must be reachable over HTTPS\n  sql_port:\n    default: 26257\n    description: TCP port on which SQL traffic is exposed via ingress\n  ingress_class_name:\n    default: nginx\n    description: Ingress class used for the exposed routes\n\nnamespace_contract:\n  required_roles: []\n\nmetrics:\n  - time_to_first_mutation\n\npreconditionUnits:\n  - name: crdb_env_ready\n    on_probe_fail: skip\n    probe:\n      - command: \"kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods 2>/dev/null | grep -c Running\"\n        timeout_sec: 10\n    apply:\n      - command: \"/bin/sh -c 'kubectl delete namespace cockroachdb --ignore-not-found=true; kubectl wait --for=delete namespace/cockroachdb --timeout=120s || true'\"\n        sleep: 2\n      - command: \"/bin/sh -c 'kubectl create namespace ingress-nginx --dry-run=client -o yaml | kubectl apply -f -'\"\n        sleep: 0\n      - command: \"kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/main/deploy/static/provider/kind/deploy.yaml\"\n        sleep: 90\n      - command: \"kubectl -n ingress-nginx rollout status deploy/ingress-n